 la creaci&oacute;n del pago de la pre-autorizaci&oacute;n</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>vpos-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Agregar la reversa de una pre-autorizaci&oacute;n</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">18</p></td><td><p>vpos-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Pre-autorizacion multi buy token</strong></p></td><td><p>Agregar flujo de 3DS en pre-autorizaci&oacute;n</p><ul><li><p>Enviar la respuesta de 3DS al JPos en la pre-autorizaci&oacute;n</p></li><li><p>Guardar la respuesta de 3DS en tablas de VPos</p></li></ul></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">20</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">124</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Gesti&oacute;n 15% (para facturaci&oacute;n, no afecta el desarrollo)</strong></p><p><em>Incluye reuniones de estimaci&oacute;n, planificaci&oacute;n, t&eacute;cnicas y de seguimiento.</em></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">20</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo + Gesti&oacute;n</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">144</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3492315149"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":179689128},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","c